snippet.title: Paranormal Cleanup Trailer | NEW COOP HORROR GAME 2023
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2197890/Paranormal_Cleanup/

Paranormal Cleanup is a 1-4 player online co-op survival horror game. This is no ordinary clean-up job. You are employees of a cleaning company tasked with cleaning up a haunted house. Take out the trash, but don't get caught by the ghosts that haunt the place!
